	 <section id="section_A0117D817D2C484CB671CED0CE19863B"> 
		<title>2014</title> 
		<p>The following 2014 goals will also carry into 2015: 
		</p> 
		<ul id="ul_E1B6C5E3981446A785789870E82C2F7B"> 
		  <li id="li_F8AF406C21CE4903B951CEC3C87E2D18">Domain move from Omniture
			 to marketing-adobe.com/help. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_6656C9ADF6BD4AB58969A9C846C28F20">Rollout Shell 2.0 style on
			 help (June 2014). 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_B3BD0B70D1674952BCF633BA0BBE0085">Display help search
			 results as you type in the Help drop-down Search field (implemented in MC, not
			 for solutions). 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_6B60183EB9F543A2B0AEA3AF2224CC40"> Improve processes and
			 procedures across doc teams. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_619E643DA6E9476F859BB71A520F16BE"> Support the Marketing
			 Cloud and Creative Cloud integration. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_E69DFB5842F040F0B64789974AD254DD"> Implement Recommendations
			 on product doc topics. ("Customers who viewed this topic also viewed that
			 topic.") 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_407EE71D611246B6ABC30062F1CD7A49"> Feedback for
			 documentation topics and articles. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_35B60AF867EB474EB8009559D1AF5FB4"> In-production
			 notifications for Release Notes and updates. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_EA024E553A1943D48D5FD6B3FC201986"> Improve search tagging
			 and weighting of topics. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_BB4A08DF66134DAD83808A1A1D53473D"> Improve writer subject
			 matter expertise. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_AAAA08270B474C5EAB1E953559683435"> Work with Support to
			 reduce or solve issues before they are reported. 
		  </li> 
		  <li id="li_BFE11484E4B644F3B3273F5895355A28"> Improve integration paths
			 with Community resources. 
		  </li> 
		</ul> 
	 </section> 
